# вҳ• Spring Core вҖ“ XML Based Configuration

A simple **Spring Core project** demonstrating **Dependency Injection (DI)** using **XML-based configuration**.

This project illustrates how the **Spring IoC Container** manages object creation and dependency injection using an XML configuration file.

---

## рҹ“ҡ Overview

Spring follows the concept of **Inversion of Control (IoC)**. Instead of creating objects manually, the **Spring container** creates and manages objects and their dependencies.

This project models a simple relationship:

```
Programmer вҶ’ Laptop
```

The `Programmer` class depends on the `Laptop` class to perform coding tasks.

The dependency is injected using **Setter Injection** defined in **beans.xml**.

---

